{"tid":497263,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"［痴線］大埔徒步去紅磡","createTime":"2017-12-12T14:19:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-25T15:04:34.000Z","uid":83560,"like":184,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":64,"replies":[{"pid":"7e741eb6ec44b55fa0a5e101ab90ecfb61b764f4","tid":497263,"uid":83560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T14:19:37.000Z","msg":"前言：首先好多謝你撳入黎。我打上黎純粹係想做個紀錄同分享下，雖然唔係咩壯舉，但總算完成自己一個心願。當初只係吹下水，講下一年又一年，今日總算實行到。<br />\n<br />\n人生好多時都係咁，往往好多念頭，最後都冇實踐。試諗下，幾多次話做運動、約食飯、去旅行，最後都冇做到。所以，心動不如行動，踏出第一步啦。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">或者你會認到我係邊個，不過唔好搵我相認啦。你知道就好，我唔需要知你知。</span><br />\n<br />\n事不宜遲，入正題。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/12/221629_3d89cd5a7bdcbb16715cb538b5d80cd4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F12%2F221629_3d89cd5a7bdcbb16715cb538b5d80cd4.jpg&h=9a2c3400&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今日嘅大概路線<br />\n其實唔算難行，大部分時間都係行平路同係市區。"},{"pid":"c348c2553c9c0be8932f96e5da8385ef824373a6","tid":497263,"uid":83560,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T14:26:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/12/222057_429480bcbf14d35d24566dde5c145f69.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F12%2F222057_429480bcbf14d35d24566dde5c145f69.jpg&h=d23147c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n十點鐘係大埔墟站開始，預六個鐘行，加一個鐘食飯，應該趕到係入黑前到。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/12/222253_676476679c0efa1368392d056dc0dffa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F12%2F222253_676476679c0efa1368392d056dc0dffa.jpg&h=7c579382&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今日天氣唔錯，幾舒服。順帶一提，我啲相一路行一路用電話影，質素係會差啲。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/12/222454_b9f705c833f1180a3ecee12c9dfb00a0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F12%2F222454_b9f705c833f1180a3ecee12c9dfb00a0.jpg&h=31f51e3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n準備行出吐露港，見到勁多人踩單車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03d83989db7870920288aa97294a21d5bc21553a","tid":497263,"uid":146299,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T14:32:06.000Z","msg":"行完之後隻腳有無腳震"},{"pid":"08bb8c463283b29185dfed94b7252013a1eeb611","tid":497263,"uid":83560,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T14:32:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/12/222858_f7133a25cba19801e345a4a823795c36.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F12%2F222858_f7133a25cba19801e345a4a823795c36.jpg&h=82451cec&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/12/222859_aa173b8f96ca9e68d949c425c0d0997f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F12%2F222859_aa173b8f96ca9e68d949c425c0d0997f.jpg&h=21b688e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n閒日朝早嘅吐露港，一路上都好靜好少人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/12/223133_0797e31d422621d378619548e6dc3c8c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F12%2F223133_0797e31d422621d378619548e6dc3c8c.jpg&h=8df01e89&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/12/223134_e0b0f512a3d9baa176e3febddd651aff.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F12%2F223134_e0b0f512a3d9baa176e3febddd651aff.jpg&h=963a58c4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/12/223134_2faa65122327d58b69b34ca04009b3c6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F12%2F223134_2faa65122327d58b69b34ca04009b3c6.jpg&h=61c7d671&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n行到科學園，用左大約一個鐘。"},{"pid":"f599140b9985e23494ab82ad5d7849ab113428a5","tid":497263,"uid":24165,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T14:32:25.000Z","msg":"成功？"},{"pid":"9bfe3830e89e7bb870e14bff7afee2bdb7a4121b","tid":497263,"uid":3108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T14:33:08.000Z","msg":"成功？"},{"pid":"cf2a2842997f48776177d67ae7e713837839d5d5","tid":497263,"uid":83560,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T14:33:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>行完之後隻腳有無腳震</blockquote><br />\n冇震 不過好攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05e4cdfabb4c131c5fd8967c6c47d8ef4a4119ad","tid":497263,"uid":83560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T14:34:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>成功？</blockquote><br />\n睇埋你咪知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"002c5b2d3ed7e8d394323f3ad4e166751912f186","tid":497263,"uid":36696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T14:34:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64e215da6c74d605f26a9935270b23806813f497","tid":497263,"uid":129209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T14:35:12.000Z","msg":"坐住東鐵推Post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40235e31728728ed889f40b104dcf5464727cf48","tid":497263,"uid":102485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T14:35:21.000Z","msg":"快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a84e612e2440dbf6c3b465bcd6798567266daa2","tid":497263,"uid":139093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T14:37:27.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"8015a378665c4009eadaad77f815a8a28e0b2f3a","tid":497263,"uid":83560,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T14:37:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/12/223547_316a0ebaf0ec248f4384bffdbf13e1bd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F12%2F223547_316a0ebaf0ec248f4384bffdbf13e1bd.jpg&h=ff3f67ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n行到咁上下，都行到大學站果頭，好似係。打個卡。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/12/223548_3cd5b3cb29065a6ad7b3bf1ed2b0204e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F12%2F223548_3cd5b3cb29065a6ad7b3bf1ed2b0204e.jpg&h=53469f6c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/12/223549_3cd5b3cb29065a6ad7b3bf1ed2b0204e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F12%2F223549_3cd5b3cb29065a6ad7b3bf1ed2b0204e.jpg&h=bb510fcd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/12/223549_0ba60a9106a43a82cdbe1075c17da0d9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F12%2F223549_0ba60a9106a43a82cdbe1075c17da0d9.jpg&h=00b5d0b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n繼續沿路行，沿岸行，行到去沙田。熱到痴線，去運動場洗洗面先。"},{"pid":"1f89eacd3ebf74db2577947512a5ac4877e459e6","tid":497263,"uid":40904,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T14:38:36.000Z","msg":"大埔人留名支持"},{"pid":"d89e05cbb6f7e13ca39b201134551b24b12906df","tid":497263,"uid":35758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T14:39:34.000Z","msg":"仲以為直播<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03ce7ba99dfb11956088ed6c51a42f73e0bbba29","tid":497263,"uid":34005,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T14:41:37.000Z","msg":"直播post好睇啲<br />\n事後講返少咗同讀者嘅交流"},{"pid":"c4327a9782e3a8b0f547a26c54a9b8e14a1c42fc","tid":497263,"uid":49258,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T14:42:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲以為直播<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，live 會吸引啲"},{"pid":"388ada493f2374942ac61b05cfa2ba4e079cd30c","tid":497263,"uid":83560,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T14:43:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/12/223952_88fbe59041553c30680a937e59faa1b3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F12%2F223952_88fbe59041553c30680a937e59faa1b3.jpg&h=7b2b0cb8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n行到沙田其實都肚餓，於是去左第一個補給站。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/12/223954_4104cf496aa04d65e745ef229f6e7586.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F12%2F223954_4104cf496aa04d65e745ef229f6e7586.jpg&h=f220b50a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n買左個小食拼盤，雞翼有啲燶。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/12/223954_3d3551d6a898306a5ad8825ca68157e5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F12%2F223954_3d3551d6a898306a5ad8825ca68157e5.jpg&h=a10ec3ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n乳酪雪糕。"},{"pid":"f927f6dec55ff391d2d880538098b251a9a9723f","tid":497263,"uid":83560,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T14:44:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>直播post好睇啲<br />\n事後講返少咗同讀者嘅交流</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好！下次！"},{"pid":"0ff69ce38227fd1e676a2e9c9d62db3c52e029b4","tid":497263,"uid":130121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T14:46:27.000Z","msg":"大埔jj留名"},{"pid":"4adb092e61177848a689bfd1c2eeb88e49a710bb","tid":497263,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T14:46:28.000Z","msg":"完?"},{"pid":"a8c198c65c827504cc8a8dd07cac14e85f658ba9","tid":497263,"uid":127220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T14:48:23.000Z","msg":"大埔人留名"},{"pid":"fb1dbdf65b7ca90ae2115f7d636d2386d5883deb","tid":497263,"uid":117679,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T14:49:41.000Z","msg":"我都鍾意咁行，不過最盡都係九龍塘行去觀塘。<br />\n<br />\n你行5粒鐘～佩服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"260a2e490f7dcbd4245ca06ba9e3a575ebb3afd7","tid":497263,"uid":83560,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T14:49:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/12/224642_b336682420bbc5d511bb4cb3abee32b2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F12%2F224642_b336682420bbc5d511bb4cb3abee32b2.jpg&h=b37dd1b3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n食完野，穿過新城市、希爾頓。新城市已經變晒粉紅色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/12/224643_7c28dcd900712eacdac79a708b494b5b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F12%2F224643_7c28dcd900712eacdac79a708b494b5b.jpg&h=3556bb25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n行到大圍，近了近了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/12/224644_5c2b0a5e7cad63ace6ada2488eba680d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F12%2F224644_5c2b0a5e7cad63ace6ada2488eba680d.jpg&h=0205ef67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n開始要上段小斜。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/12/224645_234287faacfcccb763f88d6aebd07be3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F12%2F224645_234287faacfcccb763f88d6aebd07be3.jpg&h=0cfa072d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同時亦越黎越多馬嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e230e20d86c4df996f2c79991c3e115e0dea08e","tid":497263,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T14:51:03.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"5c874131ead5660bf1c868a2eac92b93835d49ad","tid":497263,"uid":117679,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T14:53:33.000Z","msg":"巴打點解唔由沙田穿去慈雲山？應該快好多噃～"},{"pid":"ac451e93b4a6fae32204c543178f44b5a0a8d6e0","tid":497263,"uid":83560,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T14:53:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/12/225118_e2c942a5b53ae1545607cdd491f018f2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F12%2F225118_e2c942a5b53ae1545607cdd491f018f2.jpg&h=99ec0215&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n個天幾靚，影張相先。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/12/225119_98c7d5e4ef78bcb89f0dff6302103d4f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F12%2F225119_98c7d5e4ef78bcb89f0dff6302103d4f.jpg&h=9bbdadb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原來上斜係行人過唔到嘅，即係要我落返去行平地啦。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/12/225119_7b2c829506973d99e640bba80357e9c4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F12%2F225119_7b2c829506973d99e640bba80357e9c4.jpg&h=f75421e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n行到顯徑<br />\n<br />\n之後就真係係咁上斜，行到我都冇拎電話出黎影相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1af31d31b10207680ddd289309b2f819f0a2b5b","tid":497263,"uid":95413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T14:54:01.000Z","msg":"唔係live都貼得咁慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9283c16886ec2236b9d3fd9451136fe16191933d","tid":497263,"uid":83560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T14:55:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係live都貼得咁慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n打字慢對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d8086c3957b02bc6ec463d31ff37a24a2815edf","tid":497263,"uid":51828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T14:55:16.000Z","msg":"f5"},{"pid":"88ea9c7f1d839ce2a9dd26d7692ba793260ac24d","tid":497263,"uid":70126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T14:57:04.000Z","msg":"大埔jj留名"},{"pid":"520a7e99abc84ebb3abcf51b67138a3d6e12361b","tid":497263,"uid":83560,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T14:57:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/12/225639_eb1c1f64dbcbea46cd9bf9567234937f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F12%2F225639_eb1c1f64dbcbea46cd9bf9567234937f.jpg&h=d7cd8a6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實就冇咩好望嘅。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/12/225639_fc1a760c2b77bd7a51dfb5b140c6484a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F12%2F225639_fc1a760c2b77bd7a51dfb5b140c6484a.jpg&h=dd045e00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/12/225640_4afee5c430a83f9caf63ef102a3468d8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F12%2F225640_4afee5c430a83f9caf63ef102a3468d8.jpg&h=0322c6eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實都行到唔係好知係邊，見牌就打個卡啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efa6fc9a3d7864b3b8106e8d5c8f06173aa1f5d4","tid":497263,"uid":4302,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T14:58:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打點解唔由沙田穿去慈雲山？應該快好多噃～</blockquote><br />\n人地係挑戰自己腳力<br />\n唔係搵路行捷徑呀傻佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95ab33c37bca2667f44cca6adb1bd2fd8fcfc02a","tid":497263,"uid":3934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T14:58:53.000Z","msg":"live<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8548ada7766d87b3957f63f06ea034f0d3f7f3a6","tid":497263,"uid":30293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T15:01:08.000Z","msg":"正"},{"pid":"f6eed2d38bd893fd08af56e2a65c5026fae8bd5c","tid":497263,"uid":83560,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T15:01:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/12/225901_03595586bfac46baebbaa54068478bcd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F12%2F225901_03595586bfac46baebbaa54068478bcd.jpg&h=ddbc1f21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九龍水庫，好似係。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/12/225903_7905353aaedfced9dcd01f3ddf83d60a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F12%2F225903_7905353aaedfced9dcd01f3ddf83d60a.jpg&h=6cbcf458&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上面有隻龜。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/12/225903_23b4a3d68fc8c8de29e9175b32397888.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F12%2F225903_23b4a3d68fc8c8de29e9175b32397888.jpg&h=3f339590&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/12/225904_23b4a3d68fc8c8de29e9175b32397888.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F12%2F225904_23b4a3d68fc8c8de29e9175b32397888.jpg&h=cac66c34&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n離遠見到以為咁大隻馬嬲，嚇左嚇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"786d26f75c496f67010c7b8f8b2d96147dab7f2d","tid":497263,"uid":16613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T15:01:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c37c590fc32907e1bfaebc2aa421f0bce3aedef3","tid":497263,"uid":47654,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T15:03:19.000Z","msg":"Live會好睇d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7039ac344344a387d2c091022e48b3f61d820293","tid":497263,"uid":160695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T15:04:02.000Z","msg":"最遠淨係試過由尖沙咀行返彩虹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c055d802899d2496b16b9b35162102f6952e136","tid":497263,"uid":83560,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T15:04:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/12/230221_ecc10f0d038fcd32ce63f51bbf23a1de.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F12%2F230221_ecc10f0d038fcd32ce63f51bbf23a1de.jpg&h=fd68cb39&s={SIZE}\" />係到咁上下，對腳都feel到黎了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過開始落斜了。落左陣，好快見到間黃大仙祠，行樓梯落去。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/12/230222_b73f29a3d0260b690129d1eeb54095c9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F12%2F230222_b73f29a3d0260b690129d1eeb54095c9.jpg&h=69a1c656&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n分左幾層，都幾大下。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/12/230223_ef1d4af8f500847504598baa42430e78.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F12%2F230223_ef1d4af8f500847504598baa42430e78.jpg&h=75dda3cf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/12/230224_fb892c85d06369e491d36c9ccc652228.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F12%2F230224_fb892c85d06369e491d36c9ccc652228.jpg&h=a6756ec2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n快到深水埗了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2329d631674f6a5ee78b88f25f1d7e90c09f7567","tid":497263,"uid":83560,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T15:08:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/12/230555_d9f5a7a88b5765548603de3c1267e430.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F12%2F230555_d9f5a7a88b5765548603de3c1267e430.jpg&h=f650a3e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n去到深水埗，係個麥當勞補給（甜品）站買杯野。<br />\n拎住野飲行，都冇再影相。之後都只係係啲路牌同地鐵站打個卡。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/12/230555_2c659410738e5a3ca901be1bedeaa0ec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F12%2F230555_2c659410738e5a3ca901be1bedeaa0ec.jpg&h=790cf6db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n太子站。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/12/230556_da833803e9c52404a749cd435ff8dd92.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F12%2F230556_da833803e9c52404a749cd435ff8dd92.jpg&h=2a32dcec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n見到彌敦道就知道目標不遠矣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53ca5fbccae24a2e3bc4d1115df484142682b2f0","tid":497263,"uid":72318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T15:08:51.000Z","msg":"繼續繼續<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"352d14b483a4e01b2c7f908610e4f2b831acaa32","tid":497263,"uid":158143,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T15:09:49.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"a50abf335d02bf7f2f8b618d195770cd5e66e129","tid":497263,"uid":83560,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T15:10:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/12/230913_ddb2304c8c10d1b603c5b4b2a61de696.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F12%2F230913_ddb2304c8c10d1b603c5b4b2a61de696.jpg&h=5a3d1dbf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n旺角站<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/12/230914_6786b9a0a33de3aa5eae96cbfad9f18c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F12%2F230914_6786b9a0a33de3aa5eae96cbfad9f18c.jpg&h=03bd92ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n行過埋油麻地果邊。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/12/230914_8b8c6efac2186aee672d6964e00c5aeb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F12%2F230914_8b8c6efac2186aee672d6964e00c5aeb.jpg&h=b0687fe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n等過馬路，望下個天。最近天氣真係唔錯。"},{"pid":"ca2470e17a08ebc93befce5fe51ac749e53eaabc","tid":497263,"uid":89249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T15:10:41.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"af425ece7e789f97a7face02b1cfd081719a4502","tid":497263,"uid":158143,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T15:11:21.000Z","msg":"黃大仙飛得咁快去shp<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e26b17e2c91be93c16da00f3ed8e8059fe2343f3","tid":497263,"uid":83560,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T15:13:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/12/231124_2eef0e09924a30b44652779e9c0fd7fd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F12%2F231124_2eef0e09924a30b44652779e9c0fd7fd.jpg&h=31b0da9e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n見到了見到了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/12/231125_6f693f3aa6889c4a574f60e58