load/2017/12/12/231125_6f693f3aa6889c4a574f60e584cb1a86.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F12%2F231125_6f693f3aa6889c4a574f60e584cb1a86.jpg&h=7dba5156&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最後打卡，完成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n17:26 完成<br />\n計埋食野用左7個半鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/12/231126_294b9431ba673f1775d47966a8d19e2c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F12%2F231126_294b9431ba673f1775d47966a8d19e2c.jpg&h=ee1098d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n成個禮拜嘅運動量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n放學好似見到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e4f800c3bd7f1aeb22ba078b3b3743f2572f6fd","tid":497263,"uid":808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T00:46:44.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06d4faf124b38edcd89748ce14ffc8702fdbeec8","tid":497263,"uid":67649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T00:58:46.000Z","msg":"Exactly一樣嘅行程 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我沙田去大埔上咗山行大埔舊路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87006e5f33a75514dd3fd43ee1cef688af621f0e","tid":497263,"uid":67649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T01:02:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解感覺兩個地方隔勁遠但大圍就變左到黃大仙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n路痴唔識路一定變失蹤人士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n行馬騮山好似得一條路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9811e61322a0682b78a3aa6edaa4de2729d26954","tid":497263,"uid":83560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T01:04:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>大圍穿入九龍區果度可唔可以解釋多d?<br />\n我淨係識大圍行山, 係近樂富果邊落山<br />\n以前聽人講就咁踩單車都出到九龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係顯徑邨上去大埔公路 沿住大埔公路行 經過水庫 <br />\n之後會落斜嘅 會見到黃大仙祠 落樓梯<br />\n會有條橋橫跨呈祥道 過左就好快到深水埗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢段睇唔睇得明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21db2c9d8190b02b05ff944b02e3ec0e7ce7fc6d","tid":497263,"uid":83560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T01:06:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/12/231126_294b9431ba673f1775d47966a8d19e2c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F12%2F231126_294b9431ba673f1775d47966a8d19e2c.jpg&h=ee1098d0&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打呢個係咩apps<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote> <br />\n成日有班用apple嘅出嚟笑人唔用apple<br />\n巴打你快走，我幫你頂住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我係用apple<br />\n不過未用過呢個apps<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n未用過都有記錄，開黎睇下有驚喜</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n然後見到自己放假全日行得幾十步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"330be0cd0739123003688222494d9641e3cc98b0","tid":497263,"uid":83560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T01:06:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>著咩鞋行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n普通波鞋一對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab1d88109cc9dfde56bced8dd443f6d9f8e2261a","tid":497263,"uid":83560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T01:07:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>訓醒會唔會落床企唔穩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n試左 企得好穩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過小腿好緊"},{"pid":"ed9891433a684ce6b4d3ac288002ffe5af9706e5","tid":497263,"uid":83560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T01:08:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解感覺兩個地方隔勁遠但大圍就變左到黃大仙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n路痴唔識路一定變失蹤人士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係黃大仙祠 唔係黃大仙"},{"pid":"1195e7e1faf828ec1c776d9018fe9a0e54e0e1e4","tid":497263,"uid":32106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T01:31:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解感覺兩個地方隔勁遠但大圍就變左到黃大仙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n路痴唔識路一定變失蹤人士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係黃大仙祠 唔係黃大仙</blockquote><br />\n我未行過呢度，通常大埔道直落深水埗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21f21a93500c1766a477d5aa7724ca8e4a3945e8","tid":497263,"uid":130044,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T01:33:14.000Z","msg":"睇錯黃埔徒步去紅磡咁撚癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d115c525e74ddfdc509d1568346cca2b25655ff","tid":497263,"uid":83560,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T02:14:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇錯黃埔徒步去紅磡咁撚癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁都放上黎就真係痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eaf30654bbd4e161fefd25a83f3adc63d2bcb62","tid":497263,"uid":45579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T02:54:24.000Z","msg":"唔夠你玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最遠尖東行去荃灣"},{"